{"text_id":181080,"tokens":["I"," think"," the"," main"," content"," of"," this"," paper"," is"," reasonable","."," In"," my"," opinion",","," it"," is"," a"," really"," effective"," way"," to"," apply"," the"," advantage"," of"," batch"," normalization"," to"," LSTM"," networks","."," I"," think"," this"," paper"," might"," have"," several"," steps"," to"," be"," improved","."," First",","," although"," the"," authors"," show"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," batch"," normalization"," on"," LSTM"," on"," several"," tasks",","," the"," proof"," of"," this"," claim"," is"," still"," missing","."," It"," is"," better"," to"," show"," this"," claim"," through"," experiments","."," Second",","," although"," the"," authors"," apply"," batch"," normalization"," to"," LSTM",","," most"," hyper","parameter"," settings"," are"," not"," changed","."," It"," is"," better"," to"," do"," sensitivity"," analysis"," and"," find"," the"," best"," hyper","parameter"," settings","."," Finally",","," although"," the"," experiments"," show"," that"," batch"," normalization"," improves"," LSTM","\u2019","s"," performance"," on"," many"," tasks",","," it"," is"," not"," known"," how"," much"," improvement"," it"," brings","."," It"," is"," better"," to"," show"," this"," by"," quantification",","," such"," as"," MAE"," or"," MR","R","."," I"," think"," this"," paper"," is"," still"," reasonable"," and"," has"," promising"," future","."," I"," would"," like"," to"," see"," more"," experiments"," to"," support"," the"," paper","\u2019","s"," main"," claim","."," I"," would"," like"," to"," thank"," the"," authors"," for"," their"," great"," work"," and"," apologize"," for"," not"," being"," able"," to"," evaluate"," this"," paper"," thoroughly"," due"," to"," lack"," of"," time","."," Please"," find"," below"," some"," suggestions"," for"," improving"," this"," work",":"," -"," Expand"," the"," experiments","."," For"," example",","," consider"," using"," the"," quantification"," metrics","